data.name: MAC.ToolTip
data.value: Enter the MAC address of the machine. This is used for WakeUp messages. Valid MAC addresses are 6 pairs of hex digits, separated by ':' or '-'. Example: 01:00:22:32:af:d0

data.name: MachineName.ToolTip
data.value: This is the name of the machine. Enter a valid name, containing letters, numbers, dash or underscore.
